Class AssemblyDeployCallback

  • java.lang.Object

      • org.apache.karaf.profile.assembly.AssemblyDeployCallback

    SubsystemResolverCallback, BundleInstallSupport, Deployer.DeployCallback

    public class AssemblyDeployCallback
extends StaticInstallSupport
implements Deployer.DeployCallback
    Callback through which Deployer will interact with the distribution that's being assembled.
Shall be called with StaticInstallSupport.
